eu.df.jiffybox.internal

Class DefaultMonitoringCheckBuilderFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.df.jiffybox.internal.DefaultMonitoringCheckBuilderFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MonitoringCheckBuilderFactory

    public class DefaultMonitoringCheckBuilderFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements MonitoringCheckBuilderFactory
    This class is used to create monitoring check builder of different types. Use any of the methods you need and get the builder.
